    "Thus, HCAI practice must be accompanied by a specification of the organizational practices that precondition its success.Based on the review of literature presented above, there is a strong connection between the HCAI and STS approaches when it comes to designing, developing, and deploying AI systems.",
    "Both approaches have a common goal of improving human performance and well-being.",
    "HCAI and STS also share similar methods.",
    "For example, sociotechnical principles emphasize the importance of involving users in designing and implementing AI systems to ensure that AI tools meet user needs.",
    "STS theory emphasizes the importance of people and organizations when developing and introducing new technology from a broad sociotechnical perspective."
